---
/**
 * @file src/components/profil/ProfilWorkSection.astro
 * @summary UI-Komponente: profil/ProfilWorkSection — wiederverwendbarer Markup-Block.
 */
---
    <section
      class="profil-band profil-band--work border-b border-[var(--color-border-soft)]"
      data-prof-work-band
    >
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 py-20 lg:px-8 lg:py-24">
        <header class="max-w-2xl" data-reveal>
          <div class="profil-section-accent" aria-hidden="true"></div>
          <p class="text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-[var(--color-primary)]">
            Arbeitsweise
          </p>
          <h2 class="mt-3 text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-[var(--color-base-dark)] md:text-4xl">
            Orientierung, die vor „Go-Live“ nicht bricht.
          </h2>
        </header>

        <div
          class="profil-work-grid mt-12 grid gap-10 md:grid-cols-3"
          data-prof-work-grid
          data-reveal
          data-reveal-delay="120"
        >
          <article class="it-gain" data-work-gain="doc" tabindex="0" role="button" aria-pressed="false">
            <p class="it-gain__num">01</p>
            <div class="pp-work-viz pp-work-viz--doc" data-work-viz aria-hidden="true">
              <span class="pp-work-viz__sheet">
                <span class="pp-work-viz__typed" data-work-typed></span>
              </span>
              <span class="pp-work-viz__check pp-work-viz__check--a" data-work-check></span>
              <span class="pp-work-viz__check pp-work-viz__check--b" data-work-check></span>
              <span class="pp-work-viz__check pp-work-viz__check--c" data-work-check></span>
            </div>
            <div class="it-gain__copy">
              <h3 class="it-gain__title">Grundlage für Entscheidungen.</h3>
              <p class="it-gain__body" data-work-body>
                Fachlichkeit, Machbarkeit und Risiko bündeln sich in einem tragfähigen Bild, nachvollziehbar,
                was umsetzbar ist und was bewusst später priorisiert wird.
              </p>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="it-gain" data-work-gain="scope" tabindex="0" role="button" aria-pressed="false">
            <p class="it-gain__num">02</p>
            <div class="pp-work-viz pp-work-viz--scope" data-work-viz aria-hidden="true">
              <button
                type="button"
                class="pp-work-viz__scope-in is-active"
                data-scope-side="in"
                aria-pressed="true"
              >
                In
              </button>
              <button type="button" class="pp-work-viz__scope-out" data-scope-side="out" aria-pressed="false">
                Out
              </button>
            </div>
            <div class="it-gain__copy">
              <h3 class="it-gain__title">Sicherheit im Scope.</h3>
              <p class="it-gain__body" data-work-body>
                Was vereinbart ist, steht fest · inklusive dessen, was außerhalb der aktuellen Lieferung
                bleibt.
              </p>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="it-gain" data-work-gain="bridge" tabindex="0" role="button" aria-pressed="false">
            <p class="it-gain__num">03</p>
            <div class="pp-work-viz pp-work-viz--bridge" data-work-viz aria-hidden="true">
              <span class="pp-work-viz__bubble pp-work-viz__bubble--fb">FB</span>
              <span class="pp-work-viz__bridge-track">
                <span class="pp-work-viz__bridge-arc"></span>
                <span class="pp-work-viz__bridge-pulse" data-bridge-pulse></span>
              </span>
              <span class="pp-work-viz__bubble pp-work-viz__bubble--it">IT</span>
            </div>
            <div class="it-gain__copy">
              <h3 class="it-gain__title">Eine Sprache für alle Beteiligten.</h3>
              <p class="it-gain__body" data-work-body>
                Abgestimmt zwischen Fachbereich, Technik und Steuerung · mit Respekt vor Detail und
                Nachvollziehbarkeit.
              </p>
            </div>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
